quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,"Jewe Allah, Ndarahiye ku nyenyeri iyo zirenze;"
  53,2,"Ko umugenzi wanyu Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah), atigeze ahuba namba inzira y’ukuri;"
  53,3,"Kandi ntavuga yisunze ivyipfuzo vyiwe;"
  53,4,"Qor’ani n’imigenzo yiwe, si ikindi kiretse ko ari ihishurwa yahishuriwe n’Imana Allah."
  53,5,"Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah), yigishijwe n’umumalayika Jibrili arangwa n’inguvu nta ngere;"
  53,6,"Afise n’indemo nziza ibereye ijisho igihe Intumwa Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah), amubona ukuri kwamye;"
  53,7,"Ari mu kirere hejuru ku rugero rw’aho izuba riserukira;"
  53,8,"Hanyuma rero, ni ho umumalayika Jibrili yegera aho Intumwa Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah) iri, maze arasubira arayegera hafi cane;"
  53,9,"Gushika n’aho aba hafi yayo nka kurya kw’amasonga abiri y’umuheto canke mbere hafi cane kurusha (nka kurya kw’umunwa n’izuru);"
  53,10,"Aho rero, ni ho Imana Allah Yahishurira Umuja wayo Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah) ivyo Yamuhishuriye Ibicishije ku mumalayika Jibrili (nyakugira amahoro y’Imana Allah);"
  53,11,"Umushaha wa Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah), eka ntiwigeze uhinyuza ico yiboneye n’amaso yiwe."
  53,12,"Mbega mubeshuza Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah), mukamuhaririza ku vyo abona mu vyemezo vy’Imana Allah!"
  53,13,"Ni ukuri, yarabonye umumalayika Jibrili ubugira kabiri ukuri kwamye;"
  53,14,"Ahari igiti ca Sidri mw’ijuru ry’indwi, akaba ari na ho ibiduzwa biva kw’isi n’ibimanuka biva hejuru biherera;"
  53,15,"Aho ni ho hari Ubwami bw’ijuru bwasezeraniwe abagamburukiramana;"
  53,16,"Igihe ico giti ca Sidri kibonekeyemwo ivyerekana ububasha buhambaye bw’Imana Allah, ata n’umwe ashobora kumenya ukungene buteye atari Imana Allah gusa;"
  53,17,"Muri ico gihe, Umuvugishwamana Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah) yaranzwe n’ubugamburutsi nya bwo, ntiyigeze akebaguzwa iburyo canke ibubamfu, ntiyanarengereye kuraba ivyo atarekuriwe;"
  53,18,"Ni ukuri mw’ijoro ryo kuduzwa mw’ijuru, yarabonye Aayah n’ivyemezo bikurubikuru vy’Imana yiwe Rurema Allah, vyerekana ububasha n’ubushobozi vyayo; nk’Ubwami bw’ijuru, umuriro, n’ibindi."
  53,19,"Babangikanyamana! Murabona imana zanyu musenga; Laata na Uzzaa;"
  53,20,"Hamwe na Manaata igira gatatu, mbega zoba hari ico zimaze canke zica ku buryo zobangikanywa n’Imana Allah!"
  53,21,"Bishoboka gute ko mwigenera umwana w’umuhungu ku rukundo mufitiye abahungu, mukubahuka kwomekera umwana w’umukobwa ku Mana Allah, mu vyo mwibwira ku rwanko gusa mufitiye abakobwa!"
  53,22,"Iryo rero, ni ryo gaburwa ry’akarenganyo koko."
  53,23,"Ivyo bigirwamana, si ikindi kiretse ko ari amazina mwapfundikanije murarementanya mwebwe hamwe na ba so banyu. Nta n’aho Imana Allah, Yigeze Imanura n’icemezo na kimwe cemeza ivyo mwibwira. Ababangikanyamana rero, nta co bakurikira kiretse ugukekeranya hamwe n’ivyipfuzo vyabo. Ni ukuri, barashikiriwe n’uburongozi buvuye ku Mana yabo Rurema Allah, Yaburungikanye Intumwa Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah), ariko nta co bwabamariye."
  53,24,"Umuntu, ntazoronka ivugirwa yipfuza kuri ivyo bigirwamana canke ku bindi;"
  53,25,"Imana Allah, ni Yo Nyeningingo yubahirizwa mu buzima bwo kw’isi no mu bw’inyuma yo gupfa."
  53,26,"Hari benshi mu bamalayika bari mu majuru hamwe n’icubahiro bafise, ivugira ryabo ata na kimwe rizomara, kiretse inyuma y’aho Imana Allah Izorekurira uwo Ishatse muri bo ngo hagire uwo avugiye, hanyuma Ikanishimira n’uwuvugiwe."
  53,27,"Mu vy’ukuri, abatemera ubuzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa ko bubaho ngo babwitegurire, ni ukuri, ku kwemera kwabo kw’ibintazi, bita abamalayika abakobwa kuko bibwira ko ari abana b’Imana Allah b’abakobwa;"
  53,28,"Nta n’ubumenyi bafise bwemeza ko abamalayika ari abakobwa b’Imana Allah; ntibanakurikira, kiretse ugukekeranya gusa, kandi rero burya mu vy’ukuri, ugukekeranya ntigusubirira ukuri na gato."
  53,29,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Irengagize ubirabishe amaso. Uwugenza umugongo yirengagiza urwibutso rwacu rwa Qor’ani, nta kindi arondera kiretse ubuzima bwo kw’isi;"
  53,30,"Aho ni ho ubumenyi bwabo bugera. Mu vy’ukuri Imana yawe Rurema Allah, ni Yo Izi neza uwahuvye inzira y’ukuri, ni na Yo Izi neza kandi uwakurikiye inzira y’ubwislamu."
  53,31,"Imana Allah, ni na Yo rero Rugaba, Igaba Ikaganza ibiri mu majuru n’ibiri mw’isi, kugira Ihanire abakoze nabi ku vyo bakoze, Iheze Ihembe abakoze neza Ubwami bw’ijuru;"
  53,32,"Abirinda gukora ivyaha rutura be n’ibicumuro, kiretse ibicumuro bitobito bidakorwa n’ibigirankana canke bigakorwa gake kabaho, ivyo biraheza bigahunguruka mu gihe umuntu yubahirije amabwirizwa y’ibisabwa n’ibibujijwe gukora; mu vy’ukuri Imana yawe Rurema Allah, Iragumiriza akabanga umuntu Ikamubabarira ibicumuro, ni na Yo rero Izi cane ukuntu mubayeho kuva aho Iremeye so wanyu Adamu mw’ivu, n’igihe muba mukiri mu mbanyi z’abavyeyi banyu. Ntimukiyeze rero ko muri abagamburutsi, burya Imana Allah, ni Yo Izi na canecane uwikingira ibihano vyayo mu kwirinda gukora ibibujijwe."
  53,33,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Mbega warabonye uwugenza umugongo akirengagiza igamburukiramana!"
  53,34,"Maze agatanga dukeya mu matungo yiwe, hanyuma agateba agaheba gutanga n’utwo dukeya;"
  53,35,"Mbega yoba azi mu binyegejwe ibiremwa, ko amatungo yiwe azoteba agahera n’aho yoheba gutanga, akazovyibonera n’amaso! Uko yiyumvira si ko biri. Ahubwo areka gutanga, kuko ari impfumbasi ruhebwa;"
  53,36,"Mbega ntiyabwiwe ibiri muri Tawurati ya Musa;"
  53,37,"N’ibiri mu Mizingo ya Ibrahimu yubahirije ishirwa mu ngiro ry’ivyo yategetswe!"
  53,38,"Ko ata muntu azohanirwa icaha ca mugenziwe, akazobazwa ku vyo yakoze ku gatwe kiwe;"
  53,39,"N’uko umuntu atazohemberwa, kiretse ico yaranguye we nyene;"
  53,40,"N’uko indishi y’ivyo yaranguye izoboneka mu buzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa;"
  53,41,"Hanyuma akazohemberwa ivyo yaranguye ata kigabanijweko;"
  53,42,"N’uko iherezo ry’ibiremwa vyose ku musi w’izuka, ari ku Mana yawe Rurema Allah;"
  53,43,"N’uko Imana Allah ari Yo Ituma uwutwenga, atwenga iyo hagize ikimunezereye; Igatuma n’uwurira, arira iyo hagize ikimubabaza;"
  53,44,"N’uko ari Yo Yaka ubuzima uwo Ishatse hageze gupfa, agapfa; Igaha n’ubuzima uwo Ishatse, akabaho;"
  53,45,"N’uko Yaremye mu bantu no mu binyabuzima ibitsina bibiribibiri: igitsina-gabo n’igitsina-gore;"
  53,46,"Ikabirema mu ntanga zisunitswe mu gitereko;"
  53,47,"N’uko Imana Allah Izosubiza kandi ubuzima ibiremwa, maze bikazuka ku musi w’izuka;"
  53,48,"N’uko ari Yo Ikenura ibiremwa, maze bigatunga bigatunganirwa;"
  53,49,"N’uko ari Yo Rurema Yaremye inyenyeri yakaka;"
  53,50,"N’uko ari Yo Yahoneje Bene Aadi barungikiwe Huudi;"
  53,51,"Ihonya na Bene Thamuudi barungikiwe Swalehe. Abo bose rero, Yabahonereje rimwe, nta n’igisanira casigaye;"
  53,52,"Yahoneje n’abantu barungikiwe Nuhu hambere ya Bene Aadi na Bene Thamuudi. Mu vy’ukuri abo bose, bari n’abantu bimonogoje mu kurenga ku mabwirizwa y’Imana Allah kurusha abakurikiye mu nyuma."
  53,53,"N’abantu bo mu bisagara vyimonogoje mu bugaba rero, Imana Allah Yarabibubitseko, maze Ibafuririra mu kuzimu;"
  53,54,"Iraheza Ibakurikiza n’amabuye y’urutavanako yahanantutse mu kirere nk’imvura."
  53,55,"Muntu uhakana! None, ni iyihe nema mu nema z’Imana yawe Rurema Allah, ufiseko amakenga!"
  53,56,"Ng’uyu rero Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah), Umugabisha w’ukuri ku vyo n’Abavugishwamana bo hambere yiwe bagabishijeko abo barungitsweko. Ntabwo rero ari icaduka mu Ntumwa."
  53,57,"Umuhero w’isi, vuba bwango ugiye gushika;"
  53,58,"Nta wushobora kubuza canke ngo amenye isango uzoshikirako atari Imana Allah."
  53,59,"Babangikanyamana! Mbega mutangazwa n’uko iyi Qor’ani yoba koko ari ukuri;"
  53,60,"Mukanatwenga muyiteburako, ha kurira kw’igabishwa ririmwo ku bihano bibarindiriye;"
  53,61,"Mukabandanya mufyinata munayirengagiza!"
  53,62,"Enda rero nyabuna nimwubamire Imana Allah mu gushira uruhanga hasi, mweze n’ivyo mukora vyose mu kuyiyegereza ku bwayo."
